                  on 3D medical data segmentation and registration algorithms,
                  multimodal and multiresolution capabilities, and portable
                  platform independent support for Windows, Linux/Unix systems.
                  This toolkit was built using current practices in software
                  engineering. Specifically, we embraced the concept of generic
